    Page: 208
    Verse: 18
Tags:
  - Gratitude
---
Praise expands everything. People, plants, children, animals, even
inanimate things, respond to praise. I cannot tell you how, but try it for
yourself. If you want more of anything, praise and give thanks and you
shall have it.
